info.author: Paulo Scardine
info.description:
This module is a small wrapper around the Paymo_ API.

Paymo is cloud based application for tracking your time and invoice
your clients. It rocks my universe and I would recommend it for any 
freelancer or small consulting business.

If you want to check on Paymo, please use my referral_ link (shameless plug).

   .. _referral: http://www.paymo.biz/?utm_source=7b76bTP02Xee
   .. _Paymo: http://www.paymo.biz/?utm_source=7b76bTP02Xee
info.name: paymo.py
info.summary: Python wrapper for the Paymo API.
